title: Couple With Heart Man No Skin Tone Man Dark Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Two Men Holding Hands With Heart
description: Represents a romantic couple composed of two men, one with a default skin tone and the other with a dark skin tone, united by a heart symbol. It signifies love, partnership, and commitment between two men.
apple_vendor_description: This endearing emoji on Apple devices showcases two men sharing a tender moment, with a vibrant, rosy heart cradled between them. The figures, rendered with Apple's signature smooth gradients and soft rounded edges, convey a sense of loving connection. On Apple devices, the subtle 3D shading brings a lifelike quality to their embrace, perfect for expressing deep affection and partnership in digital conversations.
